(P) 2004 The copyright in this audio visual compilation is owned by EMI Records Ltd. (C) 2004 EMI Records Ltd. This label copy information is the subject of copyright protection. All rights reserved. (C) 2004 EMI Records Ltd. Mode (sic) in EU. Bel Biem. Parlophone is a Capital music label.

Please note 'Made in EU' is misspelt as 'Mode' on both back cover and slipcase. A seperate text paragraph also states:

Only for sale in PRC (Hong Kong, Macau & Taiwan not included).
